This paper deals with probabilistic databases, which are a subfield of databases (cs.DB). It also addresses the issue of incorporating integrity constraints, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses consistency checking, which is related to logic (cs.LO), and query evaluation, which is related to data structures (cs.DS) and complexity theory (cs.CC).
